(476, 'VIRAG', '{cynically, his weasel teeth bared yellow, draws down his left eye with a finger and barks hoarsely} Hoax! Beware of the flapper and bogus mournful. Lily of the alley. All possess bachelor''s button discovered by Rualdus Columbus. Tumble her. Columble her. Chameleon. {more genially} Well then, permit me to draw your attention to item number three. There is plenty of her visible to the naked eye. Observe the mass of oxygenated vegetable matter on her skull. What ho, she bumps! The ugly duckling of the party, longcasted and deep in keel. ', '  Hoax! Beware of the flapper and bogus mournful. Lily of the alley. All possess bachelor''s button discovered by Rualdus Columbus. Tumble her. Columble her. Chameleon.   Well then, permit me to draw your attention to item number three. There is plenty of her visible to the naked eye. Observe the mass of oxygenated vegetable matter on her skull. What ho, she bumps! The ugly duckling of the party, longcasted and deep in keel. ', '{cynically, his weasel teeth bared yellow, draws down his left eye with a finger and barks hoarsely},{more genially}'),
