(501, 'FLORRY', '{smirking} The bird that can sing and won''t sing. {The Siamese twins, Philip Drunk and Philip Sober, two Oxford dons with lawnmowers, appear in the window embrasure. Both are masked with Matthew Arnold''s face.} ', '  The bird that can sing and won''t sing.   ', '{smirking},{The Siamese twins, Philip Drunk and Philip Sober, two Oxford dons with lawnmowers, appear in the window embrasure. Both are masked with Matthew Arnold''s face.}'),
(502, 'PHILIP SOBER', 'Take a fool''s advice. All is not well. Work it out with the buttend of a pencil, like a good young idiot. Three pounds twelve you got, two notes, one sovereign, two crowns, if youth but knew. Mooney''s en ville, Mooney''s sur mer, the Moira, Larchet''s, Holles street hospital, Burke''s. Eh? I am watching you. ', 'Take a fool''s advice. All is not well. Work it out with the buttend of a pencil, like a good young idiot. Three pounds twelve you got, two notes, one sovereign, two crowns, if youth but knew. Mooney''s en ville, Mooney''s sur mer, the Moira, Larchet''s, Holles street hospital, Burke''s. Eh? I am watching you. ', ''),
(503, 'PHILIP DRUNK', '{impatiently} Ah, bosh, man. Go to hell! I paid my way. If I could only find out about octaves. Reduplication of personality. Who was it told me his name? {his lawnmower begins to purr} Aha, yes. Zoe mou sas agapo. Have a notion I was here before. When was it not Atkinson his card I have somewhere. Mac Somebody. Unmack I have it. He told me about, hold on, Swinburne, was it, no? ', '  Ah, bosh, man. Go to hell! I paid my way. If I could only find out about octaves. Reduplication of personality. Who was it told me his name?   Aha, yes. Zoe mou sas agapo. Have a notion I was here before. When was it not Atkinson his card I have somewhere. Mac Somebody. Unmack I have it. He told me about, hold on, Swinburne, was it, no? ', '{impatiently},{his lawnmower begins to purr}'),
