(636, 'BELLO', '{gives a rap with his gavel} Two bar. Rockbottom figure and cheap at the price. Fourteen hands high. Touch and examine shis points. Handle hrim. This downy skin, these soft muscles, this tender flesh. If I had only my gold piercer here! And quite easy to milk. Three newlaid gallons a day. A pure stockgetter, due to lay within the hour. His sire''s milk record was a thousand gallons of whole milk in forty weeks. Whoa my jewel! Beg up! Whoa! {he brands his initial C on Bloom''s croup} So! Warranted Cohen! What advance on two bob, gentlemen? ', '  Two bar. Rockbottom figure and cheap at the price. Fourteen hands high. Touch and examine shis points. Handle hrim. This downy skin, these soft muscles, this tender flesh. If I had only my gold piercer here! And quite easy to milk. Three newlaid gallons a day. A pure stockgetter, due to lay within the hour. His sire''s milk record was a thousand gallons of whole milk in forty weeks. Whoa my jewel! Beg up! Whoa!   So! Warranted Cohen! What advance on two bob, gentlemen? ', '{gives a rap with his gavel},{he brands his initial C on Bloom''s croup}'),
