(857, 'STEPHEN', '{extends his arms} It was here. Street of harlots. In Serpentine avenue Beelzebub showed me her, a fubsy widow. Where''s the red carpet spread? ', '  It was here. Street of harlots. In Serpentine avenue Beelzebub showed me her, a fubsy widow. Where''s the red carpet spread? ', '{extends his arms}'),
(858, 'BLOOM', '{approaching Stephen} Look .... ', '  Look .... ', '{approaching Stephen}'),
(859, 'STEPHEN', 'No, I flew. My foes beneath me. And ever shall be. World without end. {he cries} Pater! Free! ', 'No, I flew. My foes beneath me. And ever shall be. World without end.   Pater! Free! ', '{he cries}'),
